{"tid":1647211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"六日開花 平日和理","createTime":"2019-10-11T15:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T19:48:22.000Z","uid":96681,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aec4ea6e96046dc79b0c0db231eac79cb76f464f","tid":1647211,"uid":96681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"要有系統<br />\n依家活動過於鬆散<br />\n手足難以適從<br />\n反而會聚唔到人<br />\n希望手足們有共識<br />\n幾時開花 幾時和理<br />\n例如 六日勇武開花 平日和理非活動<br />\n好過呢一兩個禮拜咁<br />\n冇晒方向<br />\n<br />\n雖然好似係打晒開口牌咁<br />\n但我地在明人地在暗<br />\n點安排活動都會比狗mon到<br />\n所以寧願有一個固定嘅時間表<br />\n好過依家有活動 早一兩日先臨急號召<br />\n希望手足門可以考慮下未來個時間表嘅整合"},{"pid":"2e90aa1f5e019dcc439b5d8155d26d8a0e473f0b","tid":1647211,"uid":96681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9401133c789574c9f9b3615cf366a0529d75c8","tid":1647211,"uid":82253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"預早約你地 10月第3個星期打籃球<br />\n<br />\n榮光盃 以波會友 撐morey<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646298</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/StandWithMoreypeanut\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStandWithMoreypeanut&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=c5214293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/StandWithMoreypeanut</a>"},{"pid":"4d44ce3bf36270674ca3df896fa63cff4847b90f","tid":1647211,"uid":96681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972dae51a5cdb76eecd39d63dd93a62b89253ca1","tid":1647211,"uid":96681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3ada5437f7a6b52cffbde5551625859136199e","tid":1647211,"uid":96681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909b48c518f5dc90310952bf765253204d0f65ce","tid":1647211,"uid":96681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cda2c9dc384b3c6b49f579eed31bcadf6717e9","tid":1647211,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:48:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=ad4fbf45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"}]}